## 13. Lack of Certification Evidence Framework

The documentation does not define a structured evidence framework to support DFS 504 certification. This includes the absence of a centralized repository for lineage documentation, testing results, and control evidence.

DFS 504 requires senior management to certify the effectiveness of monitoring and filtering programs. Without a structured evidence framework, it is difficult to support this certification.

**DFS 504.3 Alignment Gap:** Fails under **(d)**
